{"type": "article", "id": 55250, "title": "可摆在家中的喷泉装置，还能向建筑大师致敬｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-15T22:57:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 51863, "name": "Mclean Metalworks"}, {"id": 51864, "name": "HRDL"}, {"id": 51865, "name": "Stian Herdal"}, {"id": 51866, "name": "Jeongjin Ko"}, {"id": 28152, "name": "Jay Hyun Kim"}, {"id": 51867, "name": "Lily Clark"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 188, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180715224831kuwCcet642POjBAK.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC Semibold'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The Architectural Ceramic Comb Fountain by Lily Clark</h3><p>洛杉矶陶瓷艺术家 Lily Clark，将她对陶瓷、水元素和水利工程设计的热情，融入到一座“建筑喷泉”装置中。Lily Clark 从小在洛杉矶银湖区长大，那里有着建筑大师鲁道夫·辛德勒的标志性建筑。</p><p>以此为灵感，设计师设计的梳子状喷泉，笔直的轮廓线条，经由手工制作与 3D 打印模具制成，意在向鲁道夫·辛德勒的建筑风格致敬。5 厘米网格的设计也是将建筑细节运用在喷泉设计中，当水流经过水道向下流入水库时，听起来的声音也足够悦耳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224905OmbMi5A4K8kqgBFc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714815\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224904N2vnAtSGmoRTDhfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224905PJcgrC6jFwxhYuVm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224905OKuQxh9XCefRal5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224906vr98UWJGZCtLTfy5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250617\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224906vJybDmaP1eYVW5fu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://lily-clark.com/archive\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lily Clark</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Mobile Island by Jang Won, Acho Kim, Daegwan Kim, Soyoung Ko &amp; Jaewan Choi</h3><p>市面上出现了越来越多的无线充电装置，针对不同需求的人群，这款名为 Mobile Island 的设备因其独特而时尚的设计引人瞩目。参与设计的是韩国设计师 Jang Won, Acho Kim, Daegwan Kim, Soyoung Ko 和 Jaewan Choi。</p><p>这是一款模块化无线充电器，具有附加功能。核心模块是 Ground，可以添加更多无线充电器，通过侧面的内置磁铁咬合在一起，可以同时给多个设备充电。为了保证桌面的整洁程度，它还允许添加收纳模块 Garden，一个四分之三圆形的托盘，为用户提供存放小型杂物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224948YQsizM9xNTIvPSpF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224948IxZevwYbu0cW2tnj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224948CWKtrid2g46BRz53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807152249486cLnaNk3oi4HWGt9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224948wXsN5Moeq3bfQ07d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715224948u3tXMRxoCpcbGFWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/07/13/a-sleek-and-modular-wireless-charger/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>COSMOS by Jay Hyun Kim</h3><p>设计师 Jay Hyun Kim 设计的这款名为 Cosmos 的产品，既是一盏氛围灯，同时还是一个时钟和扬声器。它的表面是一张星座图，详细展示了北半球所有可见的星座，一大一小的两个圆圈则分别表示了时针和分针。通过蓝牙连接上手机后还可以播放音乐或是调整它的灯光颜色。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225030cdLMaxeNfG1oZ5JV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225030AvpQDtaUmT0LK1gx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225030oCt0n7KTIBcVp5Dm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225030YLa1KSqkiBHUNZ8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225030tHl1XCNRvE4ApBQo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.053333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225031wdICVqneRXFUal8A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.921905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225032xdqiu1tRVlHgGZyN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Docking Hairdryer by Jeongjin Ko</h3><p>设计师 Jeongjin Ko 推出一款名为 Docking 的吹风机，采用巧妙的旋转手柄，将吹风机的形状从 L 形转变为线形，使其更加轻薄，改变了其笨重难收纳的结构。此外，它还可以与充电底座完美契合，插入后形成一个整体圆柱形，看起来简洁漂亮。</p><p>Jeongjin Ko 试图探索吹风机不同的比例，吹风机和充电座相交的接头处，只需旋转就可以把手柄从垂直方向变为平行方向。无线设计，加上圆柱形的外观，使其可以轻松放入旅行包和行李箱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225115y69rXk4WpuIMUEPa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225115altuPSVBC8RIe6G0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225115i7Xr3sKOhDQzAwNv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225115qxmXulrpBsMwNSQF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807152251168UsBvxhPWkFQHjoO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.739048\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225118EdzKpi6ejB5ty9Qv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>HRDL Vinyl Table by Stian Herdal</h3><p>成立于 2015 年的挪威家具品牌 HRDL 设计了这款简洁的木质黑胶家具。品牌创始人 Stian Herdal 关注从家具的整体设计到配色和收纳功能上的巧妙布置。</p><p>HRDL 的特点，是将黑胶唱片机本身的复古韵味和家具设计进行结合，并且将多余的设计完全剔除。左边的播放部位可以把所有多余的音源线隐藏起来，而右边收纳部分则合理打造了一个可以收藏 200 张黑胶唱片的储藏装置。此外，他们还设计了多个黑胶唱片收纳架，也是想要最大限度展示用户的收藏品位。售价 1755 美元起，<a href=\"https://hrdl.no/products/the-vinyl-table?variant=8754598609013\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225200apPVz5EsAfR3J6Yj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.817333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225200GCP4y6RAdMbHL3kc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225201GyAwBWFLQInf1xYm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807152252019hrl8tXMNs54kFKV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807152252014fpcPjnYkDAVIsil.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.121296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225201uz3lhBGdyACq72km.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.660156\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Hammock Mount by Mclean Metalworks</h3><p>两位前波音公司的工程师出来创立了一个设计工作室，名为 Mclean Metalworks。他们最近推出新品 Hammock Mount，是一款吊床挂载工具，能让人们坐在车尾的体验变得轻松宜人。</p><p>这款机械装置能够适用于 5 厘米的车辆挂钩，可以轻松固定在车头、车尾甚至车轮上，为使用者带来临时放松的空间<b>。</b></p><p>它不像传统吊床，需要挂在两棵树之间，Hammock Mount 只需要有一辆车即可，是自驾游的完美配件。售价 399 美元，<a href=\"https://www.mcleanmetalworksmfg.com/product-page/hammock-mount-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225250ADvWzfNTodmVXY05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225250Unj0Iy8VW3oX6COb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745721\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225250wPC95r37DW2IfcYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225251af80SF9UQV65reoI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.361111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225252f6bvW0kZuqPXQ93m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180715225252NtrkmFqMxo781IYy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665037\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.mcleanmetalworksmfg.com/product-page/hammock-mount-1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mclean Metalworks</a></p></figcaption></figure></div>"}